menu_deck10_3_desc = "弾薬箱を拾うと、仲間にも通常回収率の ##$multiperk;## の弾薬が補給される。$NL;$NL;クールダウンは ##$multiperk2;## 秒。",--When you pick up ammo, you trigger an ammo pickup for ##$multiperk;## of normal pickup to other players in your team.$NL;$NL;Cannot occur more than once every ##$multiperk2;## seconds.
