menu_st_spec_11 = "",--Grinder
menu_st_spec_11_desc = "典型的なGrinderは個人で困難な状況をコントロールし、場を好転させる働き者だ。Grinderは何時でも前線で生存し、相手をたっぷりと痛めつけます。また、ダメージに屈せず、敵を倒しあたりまえのように生還します。",--A typical grinder is a hard working individual, able take control of difficult situations and turn them around. The grinder relies heavily on always being in the front and dishing out punishment, being able to survive due to the fact that he does damage to enemies regardless of how much damage he has sustained.
menu_deck11_1 = "",--Histamine
menu_deck11_1_desc = "敵へのダメージで体力を##$multiperk;## ポイント回復し、これは ##$multiperk2;##秒ごとに発動され 、 ##$multiperk3;## 秒間持続する。.$NL;$NL;この効果は重複するが、##$multiperk4;## 秒ごとに一度しか発動出来ない。このパークはTwo-piece SuitもしくはLightweight Ballistic Vest装備中しか発動されない。",--Damaging an enemy heals ##$multiperk;## life points every ##$multiperk2;## seconds for ##$multiperk3;## seconds.$NL;$NL;This effect stacks but cannot occur more than once every ##$multiperk4;## seconds and only while wearing the Two-piece Suit or Lightweight Ballistic Vest.
